# Performance Notes

The scanner currently uses:

* Tokio async runtime
* Fully concurrent host scanning
* Fully concurrent port scanning

Future optimizations include:

* Semaphore-based concurrency limits
* FuturesUnordered task orchestration
* Reduced allocations
* Structured result aggregation

